FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our blockchain info discovery app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What is this blockchain information app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app is a powerful tool designed to help users discover and explore new blockchain information, projects, and trends in real-time.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How does the app find new blockchain information?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We use advanced algorithms and data aggregation techniques to scan multiple sources, including blockchain networks, news sites, and social media platforms, to curate the latest and most relevant blockchain information.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Is this app suitable for beginners?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! Our app is designed with both beginners and experts in mind, offering user-friendly interfaces and detailed explanations to help users of all levels understand blockchain concepts and developments.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I customize the type of blockchain information I receive?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, you can personalize your feed by selecting specific blockchain networks, topics, or projects you're interested in. This ensures you receive the most relevant information tailored to your preferences.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How often is the blockchain information updated?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Our app provides real-time updates, ensuring you have access to the latest blockchain information as soon as it becomes available. You can also set custom notification preferences for important updates.
